00:20:03.825 --> 00:20:06.656
All right.
Let's consider the reaction

00:20:06.656 --> 00:20:09.258
coordinate and activated
complexes.

00:20:09.258 --> 00:20:12.242
There is this critical
collision energy,

00:20:12.242 --> 00:20:16.757
this activation energy that is
needed for these molecules to

00:20:16.757 --> 00:20:19.511
