A bond may be broken.

00:20:35.776 --> 00:20:40.170
An atom may fall to the ground.
New reactions are occurring.

00:20:40.170 --> 00:20:43.893
There is energy needed to get
your desired product.

00:20:43.893 --> 00:20:47.393
They have to distort.
The bonds need to distort,

00:20:47.393 --> 00:20:52.574
and that requires energy.
The result is that usually,

00:20:52.574 --> 00:20:57.819
before you go on to your
products, so say this is one of

00:20:57.819 --> 00:21:01.919
your products,
you need to usually form some

00:21:01.919 --> 00:21:07.354
kind of intermediate state,
some kind of activated complex

00:21:07.354 --> 00:21:12.026
or transition state.
And that transition state can

00:21:12.026 --> 00:21:16.794
either go on to products or fall
back to reactants.

00:21:16.794 --> 00:21:21.753
And only those molecules with
this energy can do this

00:21:21.753 --> 00:21:26.711
reaction, can overcome this
barrier and go on to form

00:21:26.711 --> 00:21:31.076
products.
